1. *Granica* se je postavila preko grada. (A border was set up across the town.)
2. *Granicu* je ukinula vlada. (The government abolished the border.)
3. *Granicom* je hodio danima. (He walked along the border for days.)
4. *Granice* su bile nacrtane. (The boundaries were drawn.)
5. On je prešao *granicu*. (He crossed the border.)
6. Oni su otišli preko *graničnog* prelaza. (They went across the border crossing.)
7. Njegov otac je bio na *graničnom* prelazu. (His father was at the border crossing.)
8. Oni su se vratili na svoju *granicu*. (They returned to their border.)